project.name: layered cache
project.description:
LayeredCache is an open-source Go caching library that flexibly supports both in-memory and remote caches like Redis.

Features:

Combine or choose between memory and remote caches

Type-safe generic API with TypedCache[ID, T]

Cache penetration protection by caching nulls

Concurrency control with singleflight

Multiple serializers: JSON, MessagePack, etc.

Independent TTLs for each cache layer
